{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":18,"_total":18,"_totalPage":2,"_page":2,"posts":[{"tags":[{"name":"生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/生活/","url":"/async/tags/生活.json","count":9},{"name":"老文","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/老文/","url":"/async/tags/老文.json","count":8},{"name":"感悟","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/感悟/","url":"/async/tags/感悟.json","count":8}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":18}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/03/14/我的个神啊.json","date":1458002859000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":3,"day":14,"name":"我的个神啊"},"title":"我的个神啊(PK)","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/03/14/我的个神啊/","content":"<p>初听这电影的名字，我还以为这是国产的什么恶搞的喜剧，这在当前的国内电影市场很是正常。后来偶然间看到电影海报是三傻里面的那个天才，还有他那瞪大眼睛搞怪的表情，我才知道这是部印度电影。抱着看三傻那样的愉快的心情，花了两个半小时去看了这么一部中文译名很奇怪的电影。<br>"},{"tags":[{"name":"梦境","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/梦境/","url":"/async/tags/梦境.json","count":2}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":18}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/08/12/爷爷.json","date":1471011898000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":8,"day":12,"name":"爷爷"},"title":"爷爷","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/08/12/爷爷/","content":"<p>今早梦见了爷爷。"},{"tags":[{"name":"打油诗","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/打油诗/","url":"/async/tags/打油诗.json","count":3}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":18}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/10/02/第三个季节.json","date":1475474976000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":10,"day":2,"name":"第三个季节"},"title":"第三个季节","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/10/02/第三个季节/","content":"<p>秋风不来<br>漫天的黄叶不飞<br>"},{"tags":[{"name":"回忆","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/回忆/","url":"/async/tags/回忆.json","count":1}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":18}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/09/01/细雨.json","date":1472790520000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":9,"day":1,"name":"细雨"},"title":"细雨","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/09/01/细雨/","content":"<p>事情是这样的，今晚回到家吃完饭在洗碗的时候，不小心将水龙头堵了一下，于是水龙头中水向四处溅开，在我的衣服上留下了点点水滴，我看见衣服上挂着的水珠，脸上竟然笑了出来。"},{"tags":[{"name":"写文","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/写文/","url":"/async/tags/写文.json","count":1}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":18}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/08/31/缘.json","date":1472628517000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":8,"day":31,"name":"缘"},"title":"缘","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/08/31/缘/","content":"<p>一篇文章，无论是我们通过键盘噼里啪啦敲出来的，还是埋头苦干奋笔疾书写出来的，当我落下第一个字的那一刹那，你我便结下了这一生的不解之缘。"},{"tags":[{"name":"生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/生活/","url":"/async/tags/生活.json","count":9},{"name":"老文","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/老文/","url":"/async/tags/老文.json","count":8},{"name":"感悟","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/感悟/","url":"/async/tags/感悟.json","count":8}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":18}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/03/14/老了也很美.json","date":1458002681000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":3,"day":14,"name":"老了也很美"},"title":"老了，也很美","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/03/14/老了也很美/","content":"<ul>\n<li>此文献给《飞屋环游记》和《暗恋桃花源》</li>\n</ul>\n<p>久闻话剧《暗恋桃花源》大名，却始终没能一睹其风采，今天无意之间在偶像来了最后一期中，看到了其中的一个片段，汪涵不愧是博采众长，虽是话剧的处女秀，但表现出来的情绪透过冷冷的屏幕也感动着每一个人。<br>"},{"tags":[{"name":"生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/生活/","url":"/async/tags/生活.json","count":9},{"name":"老文","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/老文/","url":"/async/tags/老文.json","count":8},{"name":"感悟","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/感悟/","url":"/async/tags/感悟.json","count":8}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":18}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/03/14/重新出发.json","date":1458002788000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":3,"day":14,"name":"重新出发"},"title":"重新出发","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/03/14/重新出发/","content":"<p>当当读书提示我花了半个多月的时间阅读完了蔡崇达的首部作品–《皮囊》。事实上，我本来还想花更多的时间去慢慢阅读的，只不过今天没能收得住手，一下子就把剩下来的几篇文章给读完了。可惜的是这本书只有350页，而不是3500页。<br>"},{"tags":[{"name":"生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/生活/","url":"/async/tags/生活.json","count":9},{"name":"老文","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/老文/","url":"/async/tags/老文.json","count":8},{"name":"感悟","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/感悟/","url":"/async/tags/感悟.json","count":8}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":18}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/03/14/黑暗面.json","date":1458002183000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":3,"day":14,"name":"黑暗面"},"title":"黑暗面（死亡笔记&冰血暴S1&忠奸人）","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/03/14/黑暗面/","content":"<p>拖沓了近三周，终于在真正意义上看完了一部动漫——死亡笔记。第一次接触这部作品应该是在大学本科期间，当时同学推荐的是电影版本，看完之后只是觉得很新奇，果然日本的动漫总是会有一些很奇怪的想法，"}]}